                  reprehenderit. Nesciunt dolorum delectus quia totam asperiores
                  rem quidem animi consequuntur!
               </p>
            </div>

            <!-- FLOAT EXAMPLE 2 -->

            <div class="w-full md:w-1/4">
               <p
                  class="text-center pb-5 underline underline-offset-4 decoration-amber-200"
               >
                  Float Right
               </p>
               <img
                  class="w-20 h-20 float-right mb-2 rounded-xl ml-2 mr-2"
                  src="/img1.jpg"
                  alt=""
               />
               <h2 class="text-2xl pt-2">Post Title</h2>
               <p class="pt-4 text-sm">
